      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances luxury with dependable performance. The exterior finish retains a high gloss, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel rim\u2014standard for a car of this age. The interior is exceptionally clean; the leather upholstery remains soft and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All electronic systems, including the infotainment screen, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has undergone regular synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the most recent service included a fresh set of tires and a comprehensive brake inspection. The engine runs quietly with no hesitation, and the transmission provides smooth, seamless shifts through all gears. This is a non-smoker\u2019s vehicle that has been primarily garaged, offering a reliable and sophisticated driving experience for its next owner.",
